	(36692, 'Bloodsport III', 'https://vidsrc.to/embed/movie/36692', 'Bloodsport III brings us back to the world of Alex Cardo. This time he must battle in a fight to end all fights - The Kumite, the most vicious warrior alive - Beast. He must not only battle for his own honor, but also avenge the death of Sun, his mentor, teacher, and spiritual "father", when Sun is spitefully killed by crime boss Duvalier. In order to defeat Beast, destroy Duvalier, and avenge Sun\'s death, Alex turns to Leung to whom he was indebted in Bloodsport II. Leung directs him to the great shaman, Makato "the Judge", to whom Alex must turn for guidance. The judge teaches him to fully channel the energy in his mind and body in order to rout the Beast in the Kumite...', 'Action, Thriller', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w400/qNUI26L3BDM33xqCiXVZNEZGfHB.jpg', '1996-12-05', 'Alan Mehrez', 'Daniel Bernhardt, John Rhys-Davies, James Hong, Nicholas R. Oleson, Pat Morita', 91, 5.5),
